PROMISE TECH INC said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 43.48% to NT$81,946,000 from NT$144,997,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             81,946          144,997    
YOY%             -43.48%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            545,019          650,327    
YOY%             -16.19% 
=================================================================
 